{"type": "article", "id": 15892, "title": "万圣节试试他的作品，假面派对上成为焦点so easy", "description": "而且是那种轻松又高级的感觉。", "date": "2015-10-10T16:25:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16992, "name": "面具"}, {"id": 2973, "name": "万圣节"}, {"id": 660, "name": "手工"}, {"id": 6654, "name": "Etsy"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 232, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608124026cryjOEQ8dTX4ZlNH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t一年一度的万圣节，带点儿啥面具好啊？布的、塑料的面具已经太普遍了，浓重的油彩伤皮肤又不易清洗，如果你正在为派对面具伤脑筋，不妨去 etsy 上看一位英国设计师的作品——<a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/ca/shop/Wintercroft\" target=\"_blank\">这位叫作 Steve Wintercroft 的设计师设计了不少纸质的立体面具</a>，非常之炫酷。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124019zGCTj0PlK6B395kF.jpg\" title=\"纸质的面具\" alt=\"纸质的面具\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>纸质的面具</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124020NWw8i2ufvX0bamTq.jpg\" title=\"恐龙头面具还配有手套\" alt=\"恐龙头面具还配有手套\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>恐龙头面具还配有手套</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124020azkvOrPRSs6Fe3cl.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124021zCEDRQpOucIU8gYf.jpg\" title=\"骷髅头像\" alt=\"骷髅头像\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>骷髅头像</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124021gadGlev7IfwS0Z4D.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124021q7xQr4cs8kFd3p0i.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124022aY103uixCN8l9yQc.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124022Ie3D4jfk9GAHBwnm.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124023fq40ldeMxGFLOXDB.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081240231CcyOls5N3IVHrYF.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t所有的面具都是由可回收的硬纸壳制成的，按照设计师给出的提示步骤，你可以自己将它折成面具的样子。这个叫 <a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/ca/people/wintercroft?ref=pr_profile\">Steve\r\nWintercroft</a> 的设计师大学时代学的是艺术专业，还曾学过家具设计，他在 etsy 上卖一些手工的小东西，反响还不错，目前他正在建立自己的品牌\r\nEmpire。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124024KvEliyRICnbhg8MA.jpg\" title=\"折纸作品\" alt=\"折纸作品\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>折纸作品</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081240241QldoP9x7SKFIOB6.jpg\" title=\"每样作品都附有相应的制作步骤\" alt=\"每样作品都附有相应的制作步骤\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>每样作品都附有相应的制作步骤</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124025oxMTIus2ri8dpAQW.jpg\" title=\"相对比较简单的\" alt=\"相对比较简单的\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>相对比较简单的</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124025mwILMEsDugAbyv04.jpg\" title=\"手折的钻石\" alt=\"手折的钻石\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>手折的钻石</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/07/these-geometric-masks-are-a-fun-idea-for-halloween/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>etsy</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}